;}}s:8:\"category\";a:4:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:4:\"Blog\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:1;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:26:\"Customer Acquisition Tools\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:2;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:15:\"lead generation\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:3;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:5:\"sales\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:28:\"https://aioseo.com/?p=263889\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:475:\"<p>Looking for the best customer acquisition tools to attract new leads to your business? Customer acquisition is one of the biggest problems facing businesses of all sizes. To make it easier, you need the right strategies and tools. In this&#8230;</p>\nThe post <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/best-customer-acquisition-tools-for-wordpress/\">16 Best Customer Acquisition Tools for WordPress Businesses [2024 Edition]</a> first appeared on <a href=\"https://aioseo.com\">AIOSEO</a>.\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:11:\"Kato Nkhoma\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:49923:\"<p>Looking for the best customer acquisition tools to attract new leads to your business?</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Customer acquisition is one of the biggest problems facing businesses of all sizes. To make it easier, you need the right strategies and tools.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>In this article, we’ll show you the best customer acquisition tools you can use to generate leads and acquire new customers.</p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group aioseo-table-of-contents has-theme-info-background-color has-background is-layout-flow wp-block-group-is-layout-flow\">\n<p>In This Article</p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-aioseo-table-of-contents\"><ul><li><a href=\"#aioseo-what-is-customer-acquisition\">What is Customer Acquisition?</a><ul><li><a href=\"#aioseo-understanding-customer-acquisition-channels\">Understanding Customer Acquisition Channels</a><ul><li><a href=\"#aioseo-search-engine-optimization-seo\">Search Engine Optimization (SEO)</a></li><li><a href=\"#aioseo-social-media-marketing-smm\">Social Media Marketing (SMM)</a></li><li><a href=\"#aioseo-email-marketing\">Email Marketing</a></li><li><a href=\"#aioseo-content-marketing\">Content Marketing</a></li></ul></li></ul></li><li><a href=\"#aioseo-16-best-customer-acquisition-tools-our-top-picks\">16 Best Customer Acquisition Tools: Our Top Picks</a><ul><li><a href=\"#aioseo-1-all-in-one-seo-aioseo\">1. All In One SEO (AIOSEO)</a></li><li><a href=\"#aioseo-2-wpforms\">2. WPForms</a></li><li><a href=\"#aioseo-3-optinmonster\">3. OptinMonster</a></li><li><a href=\"#aioseo-4-monsterinsights\">4. MonsterInsights</a></li><li><a href=\"#aioseo-5-seedprod\">5. SeedProd</a></li><li><a href=\"#aioseo-6-thrive-architect\">6. Thrive Architect</a></li><li><a href=\"#aioseo-7-thrive-leads\">7. Thrive Leads</a></li><li><a href=\"#aioseo-8-pushengage\">8. PushEngage</a></li><li><a href=\"#aioseo-9-trustpulse\">9. TrustPulse</a></li><li><a href=\"#aioseo-10-rafflepress\">10. RafflePress</a></li><li><a href=\"#aioseo-11-thrive-ovation\">11. Thrive Ovation</a></li><li><a href=\"#aioseo-12-funnelkit-formerly-woofunnels\">12. FunnelKit (formerly WooFunnels)</a></li><li><a href=\"#aioseo-13-referral-candy\">13. Referral Candy</a></li><li><a href=\"#aioseo-14-livechat\">14. LiveChat</a></li><li><a href=\"#aioseo-15-constant-contact\">15. Constant Contact</a></li><li><a href=\"#aioseo-16-drip\">16. Drip</a></li></ul></li><li><a href=\"#aioseo-customer-acquisition-tools-your-faqs-answered\">Customer Acquisition Tools: Your FAQs Answered</a><ul><li><a href=\"#aioseo-what-are-customer-acquisition-tools\">What are customer acquisition tools?</a></li><li><a href=\"#aioseo-how-do-i-choose-the-right-customer-acquisition-tool-for-my-business\">How do I choose the right customer acquisition tool for my business?</a></li><li><a href=\"#aioseo-which-is-the-best-customer-acquisition-tool-for-wordpress\">Which is the best customer acquisition tool for WordPress?</a></li></ul></li><li><a href=\"#aioseo-the-best-customer-acquisition-tools-our-expert-picks\">The Best Customer Acquisition Tools: Our Expert Picks</a></li></ul></div>\n</div>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"aioseo-what-is-customer-acquisition\">What is Customer Acquisition?</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Customer acquisition refers to the process of attracting, converting, and retaining customers. It involves a strategic approach to engaging potential customers, nurturing their interest, and guiding them through the sales funnel to make a purchase.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"aioseo-understanding-customer-acquisition-channels\">Understanding Customer Acquisition Channels</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>There are several customer acquisition channels you can use to grow your business. Some of the main ones include:</p>\n\n\n\n<h4 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"aioseo-search-engine-optimization-seo\">Search Engine Optimization (SEO)</h4>\n\n\n\n<p>Search engine optimization (SEO) is the practice of improving your site and its content to increase visibility on search engines when people search for keywords and topics related to your business.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>SEO is one of the best organic customer acquisition channels as it improves your online visibility. This results in your target audience finding you easily. It’s also a great channel for attracting inbound leads.</p>\n\n\n\n<h4 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"aioseo-social-media-marketing-smm\">Social Media Marketing (SMM)</h4>\n\n\n\n<p>Social Media Marketing leverages social networks to connect with your audience, build brand awareness, and drive traffic to your website. Engaging content and targeted advertising on social platforms like Facebook, Instagram, and X (Twitter) can significantly contribute to customer acquisition.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Check out our <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/seo-vs-social-media/\" title=\"SEO vs. Social Media: How Do Their Roles Differ in Digital Marketing?\">SEO vs. social media</a> article to know how their roles differ in digital marketing.</p>\n\n\n\n<h4 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"aioseo-email-marketing\">Email Marketing</h4>\n\n\n\n<p>Email marketing remains a cornerstone of customer acquisition. Building and nurturing an email list allows you to communicate directly with your audience, deliver personalized content, and guide them through the customer journey. Email is also a great tool to increase your average customer lifetime value (CLV).&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<h4 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"aioseo-content-marketing\">Content Marketing</h4>\n\n\n\n<p>Content marketing focuses on creating valuable and relevant content to attract and engage a specific audience. Blog posts, articles, videos, infographics, and other forms of content help businesses establish authority in their industry and attract potential customers.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>These 4 channels comprise the bulk of the most used customer acquisition channels in digital marketing. There are many <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/what-is-a-plugin-beginners-guide-to-wordpress-plugins/\" title=\"What is a Plugin? The Beginner’s Guide to WordPress Plugins\">WordPress plugins</a> and tools you can leverage to capture customers using each channel effectively.&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"aioseo-16-best-customer-acquisition-tools-our-top-picks\">16 Best Customer Acquisition Tools: Our Top Picks</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Ready to shop for the best customer acquisition tools for your business?</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Let’s jump right in.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"aioseo-1-all-in-one-seo-aioseo\">1. <a href=\"https://aioseo.com\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"All in One SEO - WordPress SEO Plugin and Toolkit\" rel=\"noopener\">All In One SEO</a> (AIOSEO)&nbsp;</h3>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://lh7-us.googleusercontent.com/23Y1O2ccsSaqFsfYZ4Rq3eWXhOKq_3iDRQ3Dmt78qKRvusBNsjyv34UILgaNrlV5dFM8RZCA4bW-gNqfTd4UuTFFCvimIYDQ26zYpHa55PhS1dfxSdIHfG_7oNS-0yiJjvbN-F9_YcSTAZDKLeFxpnw\" alt=\"AIOSEO is a powerful tool that can help you add review schema on your site, making it one of the best WordPress product review plugins.\" title=\"AIOSEO is a powerful tool that can help you maintain the links on your site.\"/></figure>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https://aioseo.com/\">AIOSEO</a> is the best customer acquisition tool in the SEO category. It’s a powerful yet easy-to-use SEO plugin that boasts over 3 million active installs. Millions of smart bloggers use AIOSEO to help them boost their search engine rankings and drive qualified traffic to their blogs. That’s because the plugin has many powerful features and modules designed to help you properly configure your SEO settings. Examples include:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li><strong><a href=\"https://aioseo.com/new-supercharge-your-seo-and-content-strategy-with-cornerstone-content/\" title=\"[New] Supercharge Your SEO and Content Strategy with Cornerstone Content in AIOSEO 4.4.8\">Cornerstone Content</a></strong>: Easily build topic clusters and enhance your topical authority and semantic SEO strategy.</li>\n\n\n\n<li><a href=\"https://aioseo.com/features/author-seo-google-e-e-a-t/\" title=\"Author SEO – Google E-E-A-T Addon\">Author SEO</a>: Easily demonstrate Google&#8217;s E-E-A-T in WordPress.</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong><a href=\"https://aioseo.com/features/search-statistics/\" title=\"Search Statistics\">Search Statistics</a></strong>: This powerful Google Search Console integration lets you track your keyword rankings and see important SEO metrics with 1-click, and more.</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong><a href=\"https://aioseo.com/seo-revisions/\" title=\"SEO Revisions\">SEO Revisions</a>:</strong> Track any changes you make to your site and see their impact on your SEO. Plus, you get to see on a timeline how Google updates affect your site.</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong><a href=\"https://aioseo.com/features/robots-editor/\" title=\"Robots.txt Editor\">Advanced Robots.txt Generator</a></strong>: Easily generate and customize your robots.txt file for better crawling and indexing.&nbsp;</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong><a href=\"https://aioseo.com/features/truseo-score-analysis/\" title=\"TruSEO On-Page Analysis\">TruSEO Highlighter</a></strong>: Makes it easy to spot on-page SEO issues and gives recommendations for fixing them.</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong><a href=\"https://aioseo.com/announcing-aioseo-4-2-5-next-gen-schema-generator-to-improve-your-seo-rankings/\" title=\"Announcing AIOSEO 4.2.5: Next-Gen Schema Generator to Improve Your SEO Rankings\">Next-gen Schema generator</a></strong>: This no-code schema generator enables users to generate and output any schema markup on your site.</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong><a href=\"https://aioseo.com/features/redirection-manager/\" title=\"Redirection Manager\">Redirection Manager</a></strong><a href=\"https://aioseo.com/features/redirection-manager/\">:</a> Helps you manage redirects and eliminate 404 errors, making it easier for search engines to crawl and index your site.</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong><a href=\"https://aioseo.com/features/internal-link-assistant/\" title=\"Link Assistant\">Link Assistant</a></strong>: Powerful internal linking tool that automates building links between pages on your site. It also gives you an audit of outbound links.</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong><a href=\"https://aioseo.com/what-is-the-seo-preview-tool/\" title=\"What is the SEO Preview Tool (And How to Use it to Drive More Traffic)?\">SEO Preview</a></strong>: This gives you an overview of your search and social snippets and general SEO so you can improve your optimization.</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong><a href=\"https://aioseo.com/features/indexnow/\" title=\"IndexNow\">IndexNow</a></strong>: For fast indexing on search engines that support the IndexNow protocol (like Bing and Yandex).</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong><a href=\"https://aioseo.com/features/smart-xml-sitemaps/\" title=\"Smart XML Sitemaps\">Sitemap generator</a></strong>: Automatically generate different types of sitemaps to notify all search engines of any updates on your site.</li>\n\n\n\n<li><a href=\"https://aioseo.com/features/\" title=\"Features\">And more</a>.</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<p>AIOSEO also has many other features to help you boost your <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/how-to-dominate-local-search-small-business-wordpress-guide/\" title=\"How to Dominate Local Search: Small Business WordPress Guide\">local SEO</a>, <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/on-page-seo-checklist-wordpress/\" title=\"On-Page SEO Checklist: The Easy Way to Optimize WordPress Content\">on-page SEO</a>, and <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/what-is-technical-seo-the-best-checklist-in-2022/\" title=\"What Is Technical SEO? The Best Checklist in 2024\">technical SEO</a>.&nbsp; And if you run a WooCommerce-built online store, AIOSEO has a specific module tailored for <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/features/woocommerce-seo/\" title=\"WooCommerce SEO\">WooCommerce SEO</a>.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Because AIOSEO helps you drive organic traffic to your site, it helps reduce your customer acquisition costs (CAC). CAC is an important metric as it helps you assign real value to your marketing efforts.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>For step-by-step instructions on how to install AIOSEO, check our <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/docs/installing-all-in-one-seo-pro/\" title=\"Installing All in One SEO Pro\">detailed installation guide</a>.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Pricing</strong>: Paid plans start at $49.60. A free plan is also available.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"aioseo-2-wpforms\">2. <a href=\"https://wpforms.com\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"WPForms - Drag &amp; Drop WordPress Form Builder\" rel=\"noopener\">WPForms</a></h3>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><a href=\"https://wpforms.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\"><img decoding=\"async\" fetchpriority=\"high\" width=\"1024\" height=\"599\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/wpforms-homepage-best-wordpress-form-plugin-1024x599.png\" alt=\"WPForms home page.\" class=\"wp-image-208146\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/wpforms-homepage-best-wordpress-form-plugin-1024x599.png 1024w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/wpforms-homepage-best-wordpress-form-plugin-300x176.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/wpforms-homepage-best-wordpress-form-plugin-768x449.png 768w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/wpforms-homepage-best-wordpress-form-plugin-600x351.png 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/wpforms-homepage-best-wordpress-form-plugin-103x60.png 103w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/wpforms-homepage-best-wordpress-form-plugin-154x90.png 154w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/wpforms-homepage-best-wordpress-form-plugin.png 1080w\" sizes=\"100vw\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https://wpforms.com\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"WPForms - Drag &amp; Drop WordPress Form Builder\" rel=\"noopener\">WPForms</a> is one of the best customer acquisition tools for WordPress, as it helps you collect leads from your site. With over 6 million professionals using the plugin, you can rest assured it is effective.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>WPForms is a powerful cont