\"noopener\">RafflePress</a></h3>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><a href=\"https://www.rafflepress.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"702\" height=\"277\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/best-wordpress-lead-generation-plugins-rafflepress-1.png\" alt=\"RafflePress home page\" class=\"wp-image-163409\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/best-wordpress-lead-generation-plugins-rafflepress-1.png 702w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/best-wordpress-lead-generation-plugins-rafflepress-1-300x118.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/best-wordpress-lead-generation-plugins-rafflepress-1-600x237.png 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/best-wordpress-lead-generation-plugins-rafflepress-1-152x60.png 152w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/best-wordpress-lead-generation-plugins-rafflepress-1-228x90.png 228w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 702px) 100vw, 702px\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https://www.rafflepress.com\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"RafflePress - WordPress Giveaway Plugin\" rel=\"noopener\">RafflePress</a> is the best WordPress giveaway plugin, making it an excellent tool for growing your email list, increasing website traffic, and social media followers. All these make it an excellent customer acquisition tool as well.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Creating viral contests and giveaways is super easy with RafflePress’s drag-and-drop giveaway builder. The cherry on top is that RafflePress also has a landing page builder. This makes driving traffic to your contests easy. Once you’ve set up one, users simply need to click a button and follow to enter your giveaway. And to ensure your contests are fair, the plugin comes with in-built fraud protection.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Unlike most contest plugins, RafflePress has a built-in viral sharing feature that rewards users with bonus entries if they refer a friend or share your giveaway on social media. That way, you can encourage more engagement with your campaign, resulting in more leads and traffic.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Pricing</strong>: Starts from $39.50/year.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"aioseo-11-thrive-ovation\">11. <a href=\"https://thrivethemes.com/ovation\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Thrive Ovation - WordPress Testimonials Plugin\" rel=\"noopener\">Thrive Ovation</a></h3>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><a href=\"https://thrivethemes.com/ovation\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1002\" height=\"548\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/best-customer-acquisition-tools-thrive-ovation.png\" alt=\"Thrive Ovation home page.\" class=\"wp-image-277222\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/best-customer-acquisition-tools-thrive-ovation.png 1002w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/best-customer-acquisition-tools-thrive-ovation-300x164.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/best-customer-acquisition-tools-thrive-ovation-768x420.png 768w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/best-customer-acquisition-tools-thrive-ovation-600x328.png 600w\" sizes=\"100vw\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https://thrivethemes.com/ovation\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Thrive Ovation - WordPress Testimonials Plugin\" rel=\"noopener\">Thrive Ovation</a> is an excellent testimonial management plugin that helps you leverage social proof to attract customers. Testimonials are a great form of social proof that helps convince prospects that your product is the right one for them. This makes the plugin one of the best customer acquisition tools for WordPress.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Thrive Ovation helps you transform any WordPress comment or social media comment on Facebook and Twitter into a beautiful testimonial. You can also use the plugin to create dedicated landing pages to collect testimonials from satisfied customers.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>The best part is Thrive Ovation captures the name and photo of the person who left the comment. And being in the same stable as Thrive Architect and Thrive Leads, the plugin is bound to deliver.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Pricing</strong>: Thrive Ovation starts at $49/year. You can also get huge savings by getting the entire Thrive Suite for&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"aioseo-12-funnelkit-formerly-woofunnels\">12. <a href=\"https://funnelkit.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" title=\"FunnelKit\">FunnelKit (formerly WooFunnels)</a></h3>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><a href=\"https://funnelkit.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"702\" height=\"426\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/best-woocommerce-plugins-funnelkit.png\" alt=\"FunnelKit home page\" class=\"wp-image-185881\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/best-woocommerce-plugins-funnelkit.png 702w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/best-woocommerce-plugins-funnelkit-300x182.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/best-woocommerce-plugins-funnelkit-600x364.png 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/best-woocommerce-plugins-funnelkit-99x60.png 99w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/best-woocommerce-plugins-funnelkit-148x90.png 148w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 702px) 100vw, 702px\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https://funnelkit.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" title=\"FunnelKit\">FunnelKit</a> is a powerful sales funnel builder that lets you create high-converting checkout pages, abandoned cart recovery, one-click upsells and various other automations to help drive more sales.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Building funnels has never been easy. But FunnelKit makes it super easy, thanks to the customizable templates designed to help you get started. You can also create reusable workflows to help you launch your marketing funnels and automations faster.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>For improved conversions, FunnelKit has a built-in split testing function that helps you optimize your campaigns for maximum impact. You can easily A/B test elements in your funnel, like campaign copy, headlines, CTAs, and more.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>FunnelKit is undoubtedly one of the best WordPress plugins for brands that want to boost their customer acquisition through optimized sales funnels and marketing automation.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Pricing</strong>: Paid plans start at $99.50 per year.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"aioseo-13-referral-candy\">13. <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/recommends/referralcandy/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" title=\"ReferralCandy\">Referral Candy</a></h3>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><a href=\"https://aioseo.com/recommends/referralcandy/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"702\" height=\"328\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/best-woocommerce-plugins-referral-candy.png\" alt=\"Referral Candy home page\" class=\"wp-image-179321\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/best-woocommerce-plugins-referral-candy.png 702w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/best-woocommerce-plugins-referral-candy-300x140.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/best-woocommerce-plugins-referral-candy-600x280.png 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/best-woocommerce-plugins-referral-candy-128x60.png 128w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/best-woocommerce-plugins-referral-candy-193x90.png 193w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 702px) 100vw, 702px\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https://aioseo.com/recommends/referralcandy/\" title=\"ReferralCandy\">Referral Candy</a> is a plugin that helps you run referral programs on your site. The plugin lets you set up a rewards system for customers who refer their friends and family. In essence, it’s a customer acquisition tool that enables you to turn your loyal customers into your sales and marketing team.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>This makes Referral Candy one of the best customer acquisition tools for reducing your CAC.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>ReferralCandy enables you to leverage word-of-mouth marketing (WOMM). Studies show that consumers referred by someone they know are 4X more likely to become customers. That’s why Referral Candy should be one of the customer acquisition tools in your toolbox.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>With ReferralCandy, you can get your existing customers to be a part of your customer acquisition engine, giving you more credibility and resulting in more sales. And all that at an affordable cost!</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Pricing</strong>: Paid plans start at $47/year.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"aioseo-14-livechat\">14. <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/recommends/livechat-2/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"LiveChat\">LiveChat</a></h3>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><a href=\"https://aioseo.com/recommends/livechat-2/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"710\" height=\"368\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/best-wordpress-lead-generation-plugins-live-chat-1.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-179316\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/best-wordpress-lead-generation-plugins-live-chat-1.png 710w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/best-wordpress-lead-generation-plugins-live-chat-1-300x155.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/best-wordpress-lead-generation-plugins-live-chat-1-600x311.png 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/best-wordpress-lead-generation-plugins-live-chat-1-116x60.png 116w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/best-wordpress-lead-generation-plugins-live-chat-1-174x90.png 174w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 710px) 100vw, 710px\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https://aioseo.com/recommends/livechat-2/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"Live Chat\">LiveChat</a> is a customer support platform that helps you fuel your sales and retain existing customers. It lets you quickly add a chat box on your website so you can engage in two-way conversations with your visitors. This way, you can give your customers instant answers to their questions as they browse your site or eCommerce store.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Thanks to all its powerful features, LiveChat helps you convert many visitors into customers by helping them finish their purchases before they abandon their shopping carts. This makes the platform a fantastic customer acquisition tool that helps drive sales and encourage customer loyalty.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>LiveChat also seamlessly integrates with your favorite digital marketing tools and CRMs. It also connects with automation tools like <a href=\"https://zapier.com/\">Zapier</a>, so you can integrate with thousands of other apps. Doing so enables you to use LiveChat to add leads to your email list so you can convert them into paying customers.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Pricing</strong>: Starts at $20/month.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"aioseo-15-constant-contact\">15. <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/recommends/constant-contact/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"Constant Contact\">Constant Contact</a></h3>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><a href=\"https://aioseo.com/recommends/constant-contact/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"702\" height=\"391\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/best-wordpress-plugins-constant-contact.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-201356\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/best-wordpress-plugins-constant-contact.png 702w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/best-wordpress-plugins-constant-contact-300x167.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/best-wordpress-plugins-constant-contact-600x334.png 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/best-wordpress-plugins-constant-contact-108x60.png 108w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/best-wordpress-plugins-constant-contact-162x90.png 162w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 702px) 100vw, 702px\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https://aioseo.com/recommends/constant-contact/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"Constant Contact\">Constant Contact</a> is one of the most popular email service providers (ESPs) on the market. It has also grown into a robust digital marketing platform that can help you build a website and market your products.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>As an ESP, Constant Contact can be used to grow your email list, nurture your leads, and turn them into customers. You can segment your email list for greater personalization and create automated email sequences to build deeper connections with your mailing list. These sequences are an effective way of transforming cold leads into paying customers.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Because of its advanced segmentation capabilities, you can organize your contact lists into more manageable segments. These make it easier to upsell, cross-sell, or educate your customer base, depending on what they need.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Pricing</strong>: Paid plans start at $20/month.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"aioseo-16-drip\">16. <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/recommends/drip/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"Drip\">Drip</a></h3>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><a href=\"https://aioseo.com/recommends/drip/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1000\" height=\"483\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/best-customer-acquisition-tools-drip.png\" alt=\"Drip home page.\" class=\"wp-image-277232\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/best-customer-acquisition-tools-drip.png 1000w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/best-customer-acquisition-tools-drip-300x145.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/best-customer-acquisition-tools-drip-768x371.png 768w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/best-customer-acquisition-tools-drip-600x290.png 600w\" sizes=\"100vw\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https://aioseo.com/recommends/drip/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"Drip\">Drip</a> is another ESP that works fantastically as a customer acquisition tool. Like Constant Contact, the main customer acquisition channel it focuses on is email marketing. Drip is a feature-rich platform that also enables you to build signup forms to help grow your email list. Besides email, Drip also lets you incorporate SMS into your marketing strategy, giving you more touchpoints to convert your prospects into customers.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Despite being feature-rich, Drip is surprisingly easy to use. This is thanks to its library of pre-built templates that enable you to build automated email series fast. You can also use the platform to send welcome emails, guide new leads down your sales funnel, upsell or cross-sell your existing customers, and much more.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Drip offers all the tools you need to create impactful email marketing campaigns that attract new leads and help boost customer acquisition rates. It also offers insights to reduce marketing costs and ensure great customer experience (CX), the latter being essential in reducing churn.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Pricing</strong>: Paid plans start at $19/month.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"aioseo-customer-acquisition-tools-your-faqs-answered\">Customer Acquisition Tools: Your FAQs Answered</h2>\n\n\n\n<div data-schema-only=\"false\" class=\"wp-block-aioseo-faq\" id=\"aioseo-what-are-customer-acquisition-tools\"><h3 class=\"aioseo-faq-block-question\">What are customer acquisition tools?</h3><div class=\"aioseo-faq-block-answer\">\n<p>Customer acquisition tools are software or platforms designed to streamline and enhance the process of acquiring new customers. These tools encompass a range of functionalities, from SEO optimization and lead generation to analytics and customer relationship management (CRM) to customer retention. These make your customer acquisition efforts easier and more fruitful.</p>\n</div></div>\n\n\n\n<div data-schema-only=\"false\" class=\"wp-block-aioseo-faq\" id=\"aioseo-how-do-i-choose-the-right-customer-acquisition-tool-for-my-business\"><h3 class=\"aioseo-faq-block-question\">How do I choose the right customer acquisition tool for my business?</h3><div class=\"aioseo-faq-block-answer\">\n<p>Consider factors such as your business goals, target audience, budget, and the specific features offered by each tool. Conducting trials or demos, reading reviews, and seeking recommendations can also help in making an informed decision.</p>\n</div></div>\n\n\n\n<div data-schema-only=\"false\" class=\"wp-block-aioseo-faq\" id=\"aioseo-which-is-the-best-customer-acquisition-tool-for-wordpress\"><h3 class=\"aioseo-faq-block-question\">Which is the best customer acquisition tool for WordPress?</h3><div class=\"aioseo-faq-block-answer\">\n<p>The best customer acquisition tool for WordPress is All In One SEO (AIOSEO). This is because it can help improve your search visibility and cut your CAC as it drives organic traffic and leads. It also has many other features that make the customer acquisition process easier.</p>\n</div></div>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"aioseo-the-best-customer-acquisition-tools-our-expert-picks\">The Best Customer Acquisition Tools: Our Expert Picks</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Customer acquisition is an essential ingredient of any business growth strategy. After all, getting new customers and retaining your current ones are the only ways to ensure your business grows.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>We hope this post has helped you understand SEO content and its importance. You may also want to check out other articles on our blog, like